snippet: Milos Raonic struck a blow for the next generation of men's tennis by flooring former champion Stan Wawrinka on Monday before China's Zhang Shuai became the first qualifier to reach the Australian Open quarter-finals in more than 20 years....
lead_paragraph: Milos Raonic struck a blow for the next generation of men's tennis by flooring former champion Stan Wawrinka on Monday before China's Zhang Shuai became the first qualifier to reach the Australian Open quarter-finals in more than 20 years.

headline.print_headline: Raonic Shocks Wawrinka, Qualifier Zhang Rolls On
headline.main: Raonic Shocks Wawrinka, Qualifier Zhang Rolls On
